t\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5165}, {\"ngram\": \"the detention\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5192}, {\"ngram\": \"an alleged terror conspiracy\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5268}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5296}, {\"ngram\": \"an attack\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5310}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare window\", \"from\": 5355, \"to\": 5368}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"black box\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It reveals how a shadowy figure, known to the detainees as \\\"Rustam,\\\" directs plots in the West - and training for them - from the Afghanistan-Pakistan border.\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5540, \"end\": 5567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afghanistan-Pakistan border\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\"}, {\"begin\": 5540, \"end\": 5567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afghanistan-Pakistan border\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durand_Line\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shadowy figure\", \"from\": 5425, \"to\": 5441}, {\"ngram\": \"the detainees\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"plots\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5492}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The indictment says: \\\"Rustam/R\\u00fcstem (K) is the Tajik who is the current head of the ISKP Foreign Operations unit.\\\"\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5617, \"end\": 5622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan\", \"score\": 0.9999999990359356, \"rank\": 9.636966448777495e-10, \"text\": \"Tajik\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajikistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The indictment\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5584}, {\"ngram\": \"R\\u00fcstem (K\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5608}, {\"ngram\": \"the current head\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5646}, {\"ngram\": \"the ISKP Foreign Operations unit\", \"from\": 5650, \"to\": 5682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The indictment quotes one suspect saying Rustam used multiple, changing handles on the Telegram messaging app.\", \"from\": 5685, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5726, \"end\": 5732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1832262887341616e-24, \"text\": \"Rustam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\"}, {\"begin\": 5772, \"end\": 5780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2194625817632045e-27, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The indictment\", \"from\": 5685, \"to\": 5699}, {\"ngram\": \"one suspect\", \"from\": 5707, \"to\": 5718}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple\", \"from\": 5738, \"to\": 5746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Generally, Rustam deletes the telegram every 15-20 days as a precaution,\\\" the detainee said.\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5808, \"end\": 5814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1832262887341616e-24, \"text\": \"Rustam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the telegram\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5835}, {\"ngram\": \"a precaution\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"the detainee\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After I deleted it, he would contact me with another username.\\\"\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 5954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another username\", \"from\": 5936, \"to\": 5952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several of the detainees refer to Rustam as an external operations and explosives director for ISIS-K. Last week, 13 of the accused in this case were sentenced for between six to 10 years for involvement in the plot, while another three were set free.\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 6206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5989, \"end\": 5995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1832262887341616e-24, \"text\": \"Rustam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rostam\"}, {\"begin\": 6050, \"end\": 6056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"score\": 0.9965712144984205, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISIS-K\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State_\\u2013_Khorasan_Province\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the detainees\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 5979}, {\"ngram\": \"an external operations\", \"from\": 5999, \"to\": 6021}, {\"ngram\": \"explosives director\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6045}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6099}, {\"ngram\": \"between six to 10 years\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6142}, {\"ngram\": \"involvement\", \"from\": 6147, \"to\": 6158}, {\"ngram\": \"the plot\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The indictment, first reported in Turkish media, also describes, through the testimony of detainees, how a conveyor belt of ISIS-K recruits moves through an array of hotels in Istanbul.\", \"from\": 6208, \"to\": 6393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6242, \"end\": 6